					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Lots of classic and recent references. Here's the ones I picked up.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Id<br /> Our best life: Iris (omega-7, not Dark)? She deals with photographs that can &quot;move&quot;<br /> The black vault:<br /> Tome of cosmic madness: freebie. 1425.<br /> Money for nothing: Amos Marshall of MCD buying concepts from Envelope logistics</p> <p>Ego<br /> Notes on homunculi:<br /> Anathema: Clef's reality bender seminar<br /> Emojis: 2521<br /> Bradbury: seems like AWCY but thats all I have</p> <p>Mort<br /> Babel:<br /> Nameless: the whole antimemetics division<br /> Seven wives: scarlet king and 231<br /> Epitaph: end of death canon</p> <p>Deus<br /> Godhood: Swann's proposal?</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
